<P>
 Tri-Lite Inc.: The company said Monday it has completed the acquisition of NL 
Corp., a manufacturer of commercial lighting fixtures in Cleveland, in an 
all-stock transaction.Tri-Lite of Irvine, a lighting manufacturer and 
distributor, said it estimates 1993 sales of about $12 million, up from about 
