<P>
 Professional Animal Laboratory Inc.: The veterinary laboratory in Irvine has 
been bought for $9.5 million by Santa Monica-based Veterinary Centers of 
America Inc., the companies said Friday. Veterinary Centers, which owns and 
operates 27 veterinary hospitals and clinics, will also buy the building in 
which Professional Animal Laboratory is the principal tenant. 
