<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA031594-0216 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 023002 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 15, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
