<DATE>
<P>
March 15, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 5; Column 1; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
735 words 
</P>
