REGIONAL ROUNDUP: SUPERIOR INDUSTRIES TO MAKE BMW WHEELS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Superior Industries International Inc., a Van Nuys maker of cast aluminum 
wheels for the automotive industry, said it has a contract to supply wheels for 
