<DOCID> 023072 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 15, 1994, Tuesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Page 14 
</P>
